\begin{question}
已知数列\(\left\{ a_{n} \right\}的前n项和为S_{n}\)，
若对任意\(n \in N^{\text{*}}\)，
向量\(\overrightarrow{p_{n}} = (4, - 2n - 1)，
\overrightarrow{q_{n}} = \left( S_{n},a_{n} \right)\)，
有\(\overrightarrow{p_{n}} \cdot \overrightarrow{q_{n}} = 1\)．
\begin{enumerate}[label=(\arabic*)]
  \item 求数列\(\left\{ a_{n} \right\}\)的通项公式；
  \item 记\(b_{n} = \frac{1}{a_{n}a_{n + 1}}\)，
\item 数列\(\left\{ b_{n} \right\}前n项和为T_{n}\)，
\item 求证：\(T_{n} < \frac{1}{2}\)．
\end{enumerate}
\topics{裂项相消法求和；利用an与sn关系求通项或项}
\difficulty{0.65}
\answer{(1)\(a_{n} = 2n - 1\)
(2)证明见解析}
\explain{(1)因为\(\overrightarrow{p_{n}} \cdot \overrightarrow{q_{n}} = 1\)，
即：\(4S_{n} + ( - 2n - 1)a_{n} = 1 \Rightarrow 4S_{n} - (2n + 1)a_{n} = 1．\)①\par
当\(n = 1\)时，\(4S_{1} - 3a_{1} = 1\)，\par
又\(S_{1} = a_{1}\)，所以\(a_{1} = 1\)．\par
当\(n \geq 2\)时，
\(4S_{n - 1} - (2n - 1)a_{n - 1} = 1\)，②\par
由①-②得：\(4a_{n} = (2n + 1)a_{n} - (2n - 1)a_{n - 1}．\)\par
整理得\(\frac{a_{n}}{a_{n - 1}} = \frac{2n - 1}{2n - 3}(n \geq 2)\)，\par
由累乘法得：\(a_{n} = a_{1} \times \frac{a_{2}}{a_{1}} \times \frac{a_{3}}{a_{2}} \times \cdots \times \frac{a_{n}}{a_{n - 1}}\)，\par
代入比值：\(a_{n} = 1 \times \frac{3}{1} \times \frac{5}{3} \times \cdots \times \frac{2n - 1}{2n - 3} = 2n - 1．\)\par
当\(n = 1\)时，\(2 \times 1 - 1 = 1\)，符合条件．\par
所以数列\(\left\{ a_{n} \right\}\)的通项公式为\(a_{n} = 2n - 1．\)\par
(2)由\(a_{n} = 2n - 1\)，
得\(b_{n} = \frac{1}{a_{n}a_{n + 1}} = \frac{1}{(2n - 1)(2n + 1)} = \frac{1}{2}\left( \frac{1}{2n - 1} - \frac{1}{2n + 1} \right)\)，\par
所以前\(n\)项和：\(T_{n} = b_{1} + b_{2} + \cdots + b_{n} = \frac{1}{2}\left\lbrack \left( 1 - \frac{1}{3} \right) + \left( \frac{1}{3} - \frac{1}{5} \right) + \cdots + \left( \frac{1}{2n - 1} - \frac{1}{2n + 1} \right) \right\rbrack= \frac{1}{2}\left( 1 - \frac{1}{2n + 1} \right)\)．\par
因为\(n \in N^{\text{*}}\)，
所以\(\frac{1}{2n + 1} > 0,1 - \frac{1}{2n + 1} < 1\)，
所以\(T_{n} < \frac{1}{2}\)．}
\end{question}

