解法二：由(1)知\(C = \frac{\pi}{2},\therefore\sin A = \frac{a}{c} = \frac{a}{2}\)，\par
\(S_{\bigtriangleup ADE} = \frac{1}{6}b\text{sin}A = \frac{1}{6} \cdot b \cdot \frac{a}{2} = \frac{1}{6} \cdot \frac{ab}{2} \leq \frac{1}{6} \cdot \frac{1}{2} \cdot \frac{a^{2} + b^{2}}{2} = \frac{1}{6}\)，\par
当且仅当\(a = b = \sqrt{2}\)时取等号．\par
此时\(AD = 1,AE = \frac{\sqrt{2}}{3},A = \frac{\pi}{4}\)，\par
由余弦定理得\(DE = \sqrt{AD^{2} + AE^{2} - 2AD \cdot AE \cdot \text{cos}A}= \sqrt{1 + \frac{2}{9} - 2 \cdot \frac{\sqrt{2}}{3} \cdot \frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}} = \frac{\sqrt{5}}{3}\)，\par
\(\therefore \bigtriangleup ADE\)的周长为\(1 + \frac{\sqrt{2}}{3} + \frac{\sqrt{5}}{3}\).}
\end{question}

